title Request Authorization\n

participant "ootws client" as Client
participant "web browser" as Browser
participant "WebServer" as Server
participant "ootws db" as DB

Browser ->Server:Request resource
Server->Browser:Requests ootws \nvalid did:key\n, signs with server \ndid:web.
Browser->Client: Forwards ootws request
Client->Browser:Verifies request, \nand\n provides \ndid:key \nsigned response
Browser->Server:Forwards response
Server<->DB:Verifies that \ndid:key is valid
Server->Browser:Serves resource